#
# Shorewall - Static NAT (1:1) File
#
# For information about entries in this file, type "man shorewall-nat"
#
# See https://shorewall.org/manpages/shorewall-nat.html for additional information
###############################################################################
#EXTERNAL           INTERFACE     INTERNAL            ALL     LOCAL
#
# Basic 1:1 NAT: external 203.0.113.50 maps to internal 192.0.2.50
# iface-scoped (ALL=-), no local OUTPUT rule
203.0.113.50        eth0          192.0.2.50          -       -
# ALL=Yes: apply to all interfaces (no iface match in rules)
203.0.113.51        eth0          192.0.2.51          Yes     -
# LOCAL=Yes: also emit OUTPUT DNAT so firewall-originated traffic works
203.0.113.52        eth0          192.0.2.52          -       Yes
